  04 Jun 2008; Tiziano Müller <dev-zero@gentoo.org>
  postgresql-base-7.3.21.ebuild, postgresql-base-7.4.19.ebuild,
  postgresql-base-8.0.15.ebuild, postgresql-base-8.1.11.ebuild,
