  07 Apr 2008; Tiziano Müller <dev-zero@gentoo.org>
  postgresql-base-8.0.15.ebuild, postgresql-base-8.1.11.ebuild,
  postgresql-base-8.2.7.ebuild, postgresql-base-8.3.1.ebuild,
